00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:19,960
the resumes, which is it's all the stuff you did.
It's not the stuff you want to do. And then you  

365
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:24,480
end up matching it to a resume or to a job 
description, which is like a unicorn. We're  

