00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:29,640
trying to find a unicorn, and then ultimately 
we're trying to get people to fit the job. And  

367
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:33,440
you start to realize that nobody fits that job 
perfectly and there's too many trade-offs. But  

