377
00:29:24,200 --> 00:29:30,200
energizes you will help you find a job, will 
help you overcome these features of a fancy  

378
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:35,800
title and a fancy salary and focus more on 
the experiences such that you are happier  

379
00:29:35,800 --> 00:29:40,920
and thrive at this new job and love it versus 
