380
00:29:40,920 --> 00:29:46,280
We to map the features to the experiences that 
actually make it happen because features are  

381
00:29:46,280 --> 00:29:51,720
actually static, your job title, but if I get 
the title, I can impress others, I can make  

382
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:56,960
people think, that makes me feel like I'm making 
