424
00:33:15,360 --> 00:33:20,480
on some of these notions because most people start 
applying for jobs, but they really don't know what  

425
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:26,040
they are. And so what I would tell you is one 
is as somebody looking for a job is distill your  

