429
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:46,000
you really feel like you can actually go 
to that's going to give you the outcomes  

430
00:33:46,000 --> 00:33:51,840
that you want. It's this notion of prototyping 
very wide to learn and then using it to narrow  

431
00:33:51,840 --> 00:33:57,160
and then basically figure out the real thing you 
