432
00:33:57,160 --> 00:34:01,200
I love how, again, this relates to a product 
where when you're designing the product, you've  

433
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:06,160
talked to potential customers of this thing and 
understand what problems they have and it's a fit.

434
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:09,880
That's right. Here's the thing is job descriptions 
