00:34:38,600 --> 00:34:43,360
but it's essentially understand what's 
pushing you out of your current job. Was  

442
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:46,080
it those four quests? Are they pushing you 
or they're pulling you? I forget exactly.

443
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:50,200
They're both. So the thing is there's got 
to be a push and then at some point if  

