00:36:13,680 --> 00:36:17,720
to basically being over a hundred million, 
but it wasn't small anymore. And he's like,  

463
00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:21,920
I want to be a founder someday, so I want to take 
the next step. But the reality is like I think I  

