516
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:29,520
anything more there along trade-offs that 
might be helpful for people to understand?

517
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:35,640
The only thing that I say has really been powerful 
is just helping people see the trade-off. They  

518
00:40:35,640 --> 00:40:40,880
don't actually take the time to look at this job 
is going to be more money, but I'm going to be  

